The 16th edition of The Hindu-Young World Quiz will be held at Panchayat Association Hall, Water Works compound, Vellayambalam, in the capital on February 4.The quiz will be held in two categories â€“ junior and senior. The junior category is for students from Classes 4 to 6. The quiz will commence at 10.30 a.m. Registration will be on from 9.30 a.m. The senior category quiz, for students from Classes 7 to 9, will be held at 2 p.m. Registration for this category will begin at 1.30 p.m.The online link for the event is www.hindu.com/ywquiz2015. More details can be had from D. Sreesagar (ph: 94463 94949).The quiz is presented by the Vellore Institute of Technology, and powered by Neo IAS. The national gift partner is Firefox. The goodie partner is Kokuyo Camlin and Kerala Tourism is the regional sponsor of the event.